org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.HLAM

Interface RtUnit

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RtUnitImpl

    public interface RtUnit
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Rt Unit'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Is Dynamic
    • Is Main
    • Sr Pool Size
    • Sr Pool Policy
    • Sr Pool Waiting Time
    • Operational Mode
    • Main
    • Memory Size
    • Base Behaviored Classifier
    • Queue Sched Policy
    • Queue Size
    • Msg Max Size

    See Also:
    HLAMPackage.getRtUnit()
